        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <div class="hero-text">
                    <h1>Your Virtual Studio</h1>
                    <p>Transform Google Meet into a creative workspace. Launch instant video meetings, create virtual desks, and foster spontaneous teamwork—all without scheduling.</p>
                    <div class="hero-buttons">
                        <a href="#install" class="cta-button">Install Now</a>
                        <a href="#demo" class="btn-secondary">Watch Demo</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="studio-visual">
                    <div class="meeting-window">📹 Live Meeting</div>
                    <div class="desk desk1"><div class="avatar">A</div></div>
                    <div class="desk desk2"><div class="avatar">B</div></div>
                    <div class="desk desk3"><div class="avatar">C</div></div>
                    <div class="desk desk4"><div class="avatar">D</div></div>
                    <div class="desk desk5"><div class="avatar">+</div></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features" id="features">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>Create Together, Anywhere</h2>
                <p>L'Atelier seamlessly integrates with Google Meet to provide the spontaneous collaboration your team needs.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
                    <h3>Instant Video Meetings</h3>
                    <p>Launch Google Meet sessions instantly from your virtual workspace. No scheduling, no friction—just click and connect with your team.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🏢</div>
                    <h3>2D Company Layout</h3>
                    <p>Navigate your virtual office with an intuitive 2D map. See who's available, where they're working, and join them with a single click.</p>
                </div>
