                    <div class="feature-icon">💼</div>
                    <h3>Virtual Desks</h3>
                    <p>Create dedicated workspaces for different projects and teams. Switch between contexts while maintaining the flow of collaboration.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🔄</div>
                    <h3>Seamless Integration</h3>
                    <p>Works perfectly with your existing Google Meet workflow. No learning curve, no complex setup—just enhanced collaboration.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">👥</div>
                    <h3>Spontaneous Teamwork</h3>
                    <p>Enable organic conversations and impromptu brainstorming sessions. Foster the creativity that happens when teams work together naturally.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">☁️</div>
